snippet.title: OSSA
snippet.description:
OSSA is the bottomless well of stories about the celebs you love or...love to hate.

Here you’ll find everything to know about the cast of the shows and movies you watch all the time: from the struggles they face at auditions, to the strict rules they follow while shooting; from relationships on set to their real-life partners. 

We’ll keep you up to date with all the fresh drops from Netflix, Amazon and HBO, as well as remind you of good old “Friends”, “How I Met Your Mother” and “The Big Bang Theory”.

With OSSA you follow all the hilarious, shocking and revealing behind-the-scenes moments that your favorite films and series have been hiding. You dig into how the greatest stars came to their success and let your heart melt from the love stories they live through. 

And, of course, you keep up with the hot news about the famous & fabulous. ‘Cause that’s what Ossa, the Greek Goddess of news and rumors, is here for. 

Subscribe to our channel, and stay OSSA’m!
